{"tid":545429,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：海航第一季資金缺口至少150億！","createTime":"2018-01-30T13:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T15:39:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47b324132ff2e63a7cb35d3011b1ebf5f7945c4f","tid":545429,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517310492_ca35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517310492_ca35.jpg&h=462814ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海航集團的資金鏈斷裂危機正加劇惡化。據《彭博》最新報導，消息人士透露，海航集團對債權人表示，公司一季度存在至少150億元（人民幣，下同）的流動性缺口。同時，海南省官員與海航集團及有關銀行于上周召開了會議，商討海航的債務問題；海航集團的部分債權銀行也在考慮成立債權人委員會。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，目前海航集團債務總額高達約1萬億元，今年一季度，將有650億元的債務到期。海航目前正在全球出售資產以還債，上述150億元資金缺口，已經把資產處置等融資計畫考量在內。"},{"pid":"52b4f1095c35ca8384730883525a190964ab4b70","tid":545429,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"有無海航fin. statement見識吓"},{"pid":"e900ba8662e4f37c7fd4c629d9ed76305f7e0491","tid":545429,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"其實「資金鏈斷裂危機」同「哪有錢，你老味」有乜分別？"},{"pid":"c5e2487ed871a7bcc84e54e5fe520b06ed003058","tid":545429,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a66490071b6349c9dd0b446ea4aa7cdd9b0b9ee","tid":545429,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"一年前仲買起成個啟德"},{"pid":"f75a38c8129a70b666b7a2f44cf7ec6bee6e3277","tid":545429,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a66490071b6349c9dd0b446ea4aa7cdd9b0b9ee","tid":545429,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"一年前仲買起成個啟德"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"佢一蚊都無出 係問本地銀行借"},{"pid":"2050ce737